        <h3>Electronics Engineer &amp; Technology Innovator</h3>
        <p>I am <strong>Thaticherla Kali Someshwaraprasad</strong>, a driven Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering student with an insatiable curiosity for technology, innovation, and nation-building. My journey spans hardware design, full-stack web development, AI, and embedded systems — united by one purpose: engineering a better future.</p>
        <p>From designing VLSI circuits to deploying full-stack web applications, from exploring IoT automation to building AI-driven healthcare solutions, I bring a rare blend of depth and breadth to every challenge. I believe great engineers don't just write code or solder circuits — they lead teams, solve human problems, and create lasting impact.</p>
        <p>My ambition extends beyond the lab and the IDE. I aspire to contribute to organizations like <strong>ISRO</strong> and <strong>DRDO</strong>, build ventures that create employment, and participate in India's technological renaissance — one innovation at a time.</p>
